From 2369 to 2371, Roosevelt dated a student named Ebony Light (2347-2401), who became a graphic designer in 2370. They had eight children, Kiara (2370-after 2404), Audrey (2370-after 2404), Duke (2370-after 2404), Derek (2370-after 2404), Carrie (2370-after 2404), Chip (2370-after 2404), Lonnie (2370-after 2404), and [[Eduardo Roosevelt]].
